# Frontend UI Rules

## Design system

- shadcn/ui (New York) + Tailwind CSS 4
- Geist Sans / Geist Mono fonts
- Support light and dark via `next-themes`
- Environment shown as color-coded pill in top bar — always visible

## UX patterns

- List → detail navigation for Tests, Shared Steps, Runs
- Optimistic updates on delete; toast on success/error
- Skeleton loaders during fetch; empty states with primary CTA
- Drag-and-drop step reorder in test editor

## State

- TanStack Query for server data
- URL search params for filters (`?environmentId=`, `?status=`)
- Active environment in React context + localStorage persistence

## Accessibility

- Keyboard navigable step list
- `aria-label` on icon-only buttons
- Focus visible on all interactive elements
